No. 10-242. Fazal Mahmood Dada, et al., Petitioners v. Eric H. Holder, Jr., Attorney General. 562 U.S. 977, 131 S. Ct. 475,

178 L. Ed. 2d 315,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7891. October 12, 2010.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.

Justice Sotomayor took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 361 Fed. Appx. 254.
